<http://vocab.linkeddata.es/datosabiertos/def/oferta-inmobiliaria/propertyType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Property indicating the type of real estate property in the listing (e.g., local, office, warehouse, dwelling, plot). Reuses the Spanish Cadastre use vocabulary."@en .
